Package validation.validators

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ContentTypeValidator
    Validates a String field used to indicate a content type of a Post to ensure that it is a valid content type String.
    ExistentOwnerValidator
    Validates a Long representing the id of a User that should already exist.
    ExistentPostValidator
    Validates a Long representing the id of a Post that should already exist.
    ExistentSkillLevelValidator
    Validates a data wrapper for identifying a skill level that already exists.
    ExistentTagValidator
    Validates a data wrapper for identifying a tag that already exists.
    MatchedTagValidator
    Class to validate a data wrapper for updating a Tag.
    NewSkillLevelValidator
    Validates a data wrapper for creating a new SkillLevel.
    NewTagValidator
    Validates a data wrapper for creating a new Tag.
    NullChecksValidator
    Validation class that ensures that the object of the Class to which it is applied, as well as any indicated fields, are not null.
    TitleValidator
    Class to validate a String that will serve as a Post title.
    UniqueListValidator
    Class to validate a list of TagApplications.
    UnmatchedTagValidator
    Class to validate a data wrapper and ensure that the given Tag has not yet been applied to the given Post.
    UpdatedPostValidator
    Class to validate a data wrapper for updating a Post.
    UpdatedTagValidator
    Class to validate a data wrapper for updating a Tag as it is applied to a Post.
    UpdateExistingSkillLevelValidator
    Class to validate a data wrapper for updating a SkillLevel.
    UpdateTagValidator
    Class to validate a data wrapper for updating a Tag.
